
This folder contains two dictionaries.
Both are derived from Pleiades, namely the "names" table.

to generate them, use:

<prepare_dict.py> and <pleiades_names_simplified.csv>

ATTENTION: the stemming algorithm used to generate the dictionaries MUST be the same used in the java in method
"stemString"
--------

The XML file contains the dictionary used for detection by "dictNamedEntityFinder" method

It contains the stemmed forms according to the specifications of OpenNLP tagdicts.
Each entity is divided in tokens: one entry per entity, but one token for each token of the entity

--------

the CSV file cpntains the NEL dictionary

it contains a unique key, a stemmed entity name, and several possible links

Thus Alexandiri(a) will be present once, but with all possible links next to it.
